# GitHub CLI account

Before any `gh` command in this repository (PRs, issues, checks, releases, etc.), ensure the active account is `tmwclaxton`:

```bash
gh auth switch -u tmwclaxton
```

Verify with `gh auth status` if unsure. Do not use the default `tobyclaxton` account for GitHub operations here.
